pages.text: # John Smith Senior Software Engineer ## Contact Information - Email: john.smith@email.com - Phone: +44 20 1234 5678 - LinkedIn: https://linkedin.com/in/johnsmith - GitHub: https://github.com/johnsmith - Location: London, United Kingdom ## Professional Experience ### Senior Software Engineer | Tech Corp Ltd **London, UK** | January 2021 - Present - Led development of microservices architecture serving 2M+ users - Implemented CI/CD pipelines reducing deployment time by 60% - Mentored team of 5 junior engineers - Technologies: Python, Go, AWS, Kubernetes, PostgreSQL ### Software Engineer | Digital Solutions Inc **London, UK** | March 2018 - December 2020 - Developed RESTful APIs for mobile applications - Optimized database queries improving performance by 40% - Collaborated with cross-functional teams on product features - Technologies: Python, Django, React, MySQL ### Junior Developer | StartUp Co **London, UK** | June 2016 - February 2018 - Built web applications using modern JavaScript frameworks - Participated in agile development process - Technologies: JavaScript, Node.js, MongoDB ## Education ### BSc Computer Science **University of London** | 2013 - 2016 - First Class Honours - Final Project: Machine Learning for Image Recognition ## Skills - Languages: Python, JavaScript, Go, Java, SQL - Frameworks: Django, FastAPI, React, Node.js - Cloud: AWS, Google Cloud Platform, Azure - Tools: Docker, Kubernetes, Git, Jenkins - Databases: PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis ## Certifications - AWS Certified Solutions Architect (2022) - Certified Kubernetes Administrator (2021) ## Summary Experienced software engineer with 7+ years of professional experience building scalable web applications and distributed systems. Strong expertise in backend development, cloud infrastructure, and team leadership. Passionate about clean code, test-driven development, and mentoring junior developers.
